values:
I have been so busy. Afterall, I have all these fucking tests and all. i am sorry, but I am not quite sure I can handle an LJ right now, I have no time really. I love you all, and even know I have known you guys for only a while, I will miss you on LJ. i am closing this journal for a while, maybe I will open it back up someday, maybe in a month or two. You can always IM me whenever you want. i will talk to all of you, i promise. thanks for all the comments and everything else. <3

-cody-

CODY'S BACK, THAT'S WHO! I missed you all so much. No joke. I really did. My new computer really.. sucks. It's so fucking slow. I waited 15 minutes for this page to load. I am sorry, but I won't be able to comment as much as I used to anymore. I have been so busy! I have to go to work now, but I will update / comment on everyone's LJs when I get back.. around five. Love you all, hope you guys had a great Christmas! <3

-Cody

P.S. My new screen name is DobermanPharraoh. IM ME!

I am at a friend's typing this right now.

My computer broke.

I am getting a new one for X-Mas.. won't be able to update until the 25th.

Sorry to worry you all! Had no time before. Love you, LJ buddies <3

Happy Holidays.

Thanks everyone for adding me to their friends list! I feel so loved! :D

Now, I took this idea from .

Spam me.

I want to get about 650 comments on this entry. Six hundred fifty. Do you think we can do it?!

Let's do it! ^_^

Post lyrics, random things, pictures.. ANYTHING.

Let's goooo.

Well, sence I was away from LJ all summer long, let me fill you in on a few things.

  • I did something stupid to Rob which I will never forgive myself for.
  • Woke up in a hospital bed three times.
  • Got sent to the MI for two weeks.
  • Tried to be friends with my dad again, but he shunned me off because of my sexuality.
  • Melissa almost burned the house down because she left a candle lit.
  • Broke my arm because I jumped off my roof into the pool (not such a smart idea).
  • Got burned at Ozzfest.
  • Most of the bands at Ozzfest sucked, anyway.
  • Found out that somehow I am related to Matt Damon. (second cousin once removed or some shit like that? I don't know.)

And that's about it. Not much of an entry, but I post a lot because I have no life.

Cody's back, that's who's back! My old account was . I took a nice big mental vacation. Life's been going normally. Melissa still tries to poison me, dad's a jerk who doesn't pay child support, mom's never home, me and Ryan are still in love, me and Roberta are still best friends, I got my first CAR.. A ELANTRA! See, look how sexy it is!

Now at least I can drive where I want instead of walking all the frickin time. Look at that hot negro. Damn. Doing okay in school, I guess. 96.374 average... kind of dissapointed, because I know I can do better than that. Oh well, A+ and above is good, I guess. I start my new job at CVS soon. I am excited! I hope that some of you guys still remeber me in the communities ::crosses fingers:: Well, hope all is well with everyone, g'night.
